field.div:


                        Property Listing Information


Dear {{ object.buyer_id.name if object.buyer_id else 'Prospective Buyer' }},

We are pleased to share the details of the following property:




                            Property Name
                            {{ object.name }}



                            Postcode
                            {{ object.postcode or 'N/A' }}



                            Expected Price
                            {{ object.expected_price }} {{ object.currency_id.name }}



                            Bedrooms
                            {{ object.bedrooms }}



                            Living Area
                            {{ object.living_area }} sqm



                            Total Area
                            {{ object.total_area }} sqm



                            Available From
                            {{ object.date_availability or 'Immediately' }}



                            Property Type
                            {{ object.type_id.name if object.type_id else 'N/A' }}



                            Garden
                            {{ 'Yes' if object.garden else 'No' }}



                            Garage
                            {{ 'Yes' if object.garage else 'No' }}



                    {% if object.description %}

Description


                        {{ object.description }}

                    {% endif %}



                        For further information or to schedule a viewing, please don't hesitate to contact us.



                        Best Regards,

                        {{ user.name }}

                        {{ user.email or '' }}
